Collections.rule:
Individual: @A*
    Types: Hotel
    Facts: 
        hotelID @A* (xsd:integer),
        hotelName @B*,
        countryID @C* (xsd:integer),
        hotelDescription @D*,
        hotelAddress @E*,
        hotelLat @F* (xsd:decimal),
        hotelLon @G* (xsd:decimal),
        hotelURL @H*,
        hotelReviewScore @I* (xsd:decimal),
        hotelReviewNumber @J* (xsd:integer),
        hotelReviewCategoricalScore @K*
